# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Option A: Official Datadog Managed MCP Server (recommended)
# No local setup. OAuth login. Works with Cursor, Claude Desktop,
# Claude Code, OpenAI Codex CLI.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
 
# Add to MCP client config (e.g. .cursor/mcp.json or claude_desktop_config.json):
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "datadog": {
      "type": "http",
      "url": "https://mcp.datadoghq.com/api/unstable/mcp-server/mcp"
    }
  }
}
 
# Toolset-specific (APM + LLM Observability only — saves context window):
# https://mcp.datadoghq.com/api/unstable/mcp-server/mcp?toolsets=apm,llm-observability
